OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FThe government has announced plans to
OL,8,Fremove a cap on new faith-based free
OL,9,Fschools which currently stops them
OL,10,Ffrom selecting more than half of
OL,11,Fpupils on the grounds of religion.
OL,13,FMinisters hope that lifting the cap on
OL,14,Ffaith-based admissions, which applies
OL,15,Fto new faith free schools in England,
OL,16,Fwill create more school places for
OL,17,Fpupils.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/18
