OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F302A1714546904
OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FBut campaigners and education union
OL,8,Fleaders said going ahead with the
OL,9,Fplans would be a "retrograde step" and
OL,10,F"wrongheaded" as they argued that more
OL,11,Ffaith schools will exacerbate
OL,12,F"discrimination, division and
OL,13,Fdisadvantage".
OL,15,FThe Department for Education (DfE)
OL,16,Fwill launch a consultation on removing
OL,17,Fthe 50% cap on Wednesday, alongside
OL,18,Fproposals to create faith-based
OL,19,Facademies for children with special
OL,20,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,21,F(Send).
