OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FUnder the current rules, a new free
OL,8,Fschool with religious character must
OL,9,Fallocate at least 50% of its places to
OL,10,Fpupils without reference to their
OL,11,Ffaith if they are oversubscribed.
OL,13,FThe Catholic Education Service has
OL,14,Fpreviously argued that the rule
OL,15,Feffectively banned the opening of any
OL,16,Fnew Catholic free schools as turning
OL,17,Faway Catholic pupils would be against
OL,18,Fcanon law.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
