OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FBut if the cap is removed,
OL,8,Foversubscribed faith-based free
OL,9,Fschools will be able to select up to
OL,10,F100% of their intake based on pupils'
OL,11,Freligious belief.
OL,13,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan,
OL,14,Fwho attended a Catholic school, said
OL,15,Fshe had seen first-hand how values and
OL,16,Fstandards in faith schools "often give
OL,17,Fyoung people a brilliant start in
OL,18,Flife".
