OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FShe said: "Faith groups run some of
OL,8,Fthe best schools in the country,
OL,9,Fincluding in some of the most
OL,10,Fdisadvantaged areas, and it's
OL,11,Fabsolutely right we support them to
OL,12,Funleash that potential even further `
OL,13,Fincluding through the creation of the
OL,14,Ffirst ever faith academies for
OL,15,Fchildren with special educational
OL,16,Fneeds."
