OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FIt is understood that existing faith-
OL,8,Fbased free schools ` which currently
OL,9,Fhave to adhere to the 50% rule if
OL,10,Foversubscribed ` will be able to apply
OL,11,Fto have the cap lifted if the
OL,12,FGovernment's plans are given the green
OL,13,Flight.
OL,15,FThe consultation, being held by the
OL,16,FDfE, will also explore how to improve
OL,17,Fprovision for Send children by opening
OL,18,Fspecial faith academies.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/18
