OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FIt is currently not possible for
OL,8,Fspecial schools to open as academies
OL,9,Fand be designated with faith status,
OL,10,Fthe DfE said.
OL,12,FAndrew Copson, chief executive of
OL,13,FHumanists UK, said: "The proposal to
OL,14,Fallow 100% religious discrimination in
OL,15,Fnew state faith schools will increase
OL,16,Freligious and racial segregation in
OL,17,Four schools at a time when integration
OL,18,Fand cohesion has never been more
OL,19,Fimportant.
OL,26,@uD@UOU
