OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,F"It will further disadvantage poorer
OL,8,Ffamilies, non-religious families, and
OL,9,Ffamilies of the 'wrong' religion."
OL,11,FStephen Evans, chief executive of the
OL,12,FNational Secular Society (NSS), said
OL,13,Flifting the cap would only "exacerbate
OL,14,Fthe discrimination, division, and
OL,15,Fdisadvantage that faith based
OL,16,Feducation encourages".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@bO]uD@\OUxD@UO]
