OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FHe said: "Allowing new faith academies
OL,8,Fto apply 100% religious selection
OL,9,Fwould be entirely wrongheaded and run
OL,10,Fcontrary to values that should be at
OL,11,Fthe heart of our society."
OL,13,FSimon Barrow, chair of the Accord
OL,14,FCoalition ` the alliance of religious
OL,15,Fand non-religious groups and voices
OL,16,Fworking for fully inclusive education,
OL,17,Fadded that scrapping the cap would be
OL,18,F"an enormously retrograde step".
