OL,7,FThe vast majority of faith schools in
OL,8,FEngland are Christian ` mostly Church
OL,9,Fof England (CofE) or Roman Catholic,
OL,10,Fbut there are also a small number of
OL,11,FJewish, Muslim, Hindu, or Sikh schools.
