OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FNigel Genders, chief education officer
OL,8,Fof the CofE, said: "This broad package
OL,9,Fis good news because it will mean more
OL,10,Fpeople can benefit from the education
OL,11,Fprovided by Church of England schools
OL,12,Fwhich is so highly valued by parents
OL,13,Fand children and young people.
OL,15,F"By enabling Church of England special
OL,16,Fschools, we can serve the needs of
OL,17,Fmore children in more communities,
OL,18,Firrespective of their faith
OL,19,Fbackground."
