OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FReplacing the 50% rule for faith-based
OL,8,Ffree schools was originally suggested
OL,9,Fin September 2016 when the Government
OL,10,Flaunched a consultation on expanding
OL,11,Fthe number of good school places
OL,12,Favailable.
OL,14,FThe Conservatives then set out a
OL,15,Fcommitment to "replace the unfair and
OL,16,Fineffective inclusivity rules" that
OL,17,Fprevent the establishment of new
OL,18,FCatholic schools in their 2017
OL,19,Fmanifesto.
OL,26,@wD@OOUxD@^O]
