OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FBut in May 2018, the Government
OL,8,Fdecided to retain the 50% cap on
OL,9,Freligious-based admissions to new free
OL,10,Fschools.
OL,12,FInstead, it announced a capital scheme
OL,13,Fto support the creation of new
OL,14,Fvoluntary aided (VA) schools ` which
OL,15,Fare run with local council involvement
OL,16,Fand can be 100% selective on pupils'
OL,17,Freligion.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G14/18
