OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,8,Fthe NAHT school leaders' union, said
OL,9,Fit was worried that removing the cap
OL,10,Fis "an unnecessary and potentially
OL,11,Fretrograde step."
OL,13,FHe said: "We are concerned that there
OL,14,Fis a danger that such a move could
OL,15,Finadvertently lead to a sense of
OL,16,Fselection through the back door and
OL,17,Fcould potentially make it harder for
OL,18,Fsome pupils to get a place at their
OL,19,Flocal school.
OL,26,@rD@DOUsD@QO]uD@JOU
