OL,3,CCap on faith-based admissions into
OL,4,Cschools to be lifted under government
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,F"Such a change in policy feels
OL,8,Finappropriate so close to an election
OL,9,Fand is something that should be
OL,10,Fincorporated into a manifesto."
OL,12,FPepe Di'Iasio, general secretary of
OL,13,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,14,FLeaders (ASCL), added it has seen no
OL,15,Fevidence that scrapping the 50% cap
OL,16,Fwould be "of social or educational
OL,17,Fbenefit".
