OL,7,FSir Edward Leigh, former president of
OL,8,Fthe Catholic Union and Tory MP for
OL,9,FGainsborough, called for the cap to be
OL,10,Fremoved before the upcoming general
OL,11,Felection as he said it would make a
OL,12,F"big difference" to the Catholic
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,15,FHe said: "This is a great victory for
OL,16,FCatholic education and common sense.
OL,17,FFor years, we have been trying to make
OL,18,Fministers see sense on this and allow
OL,19,FCatholic free schools to open."
